  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to validate a newly designed self-help treatment for
      nightmares. This self-help treatment is based on Imagery Rehearsal Therapy. This treatment
      will be validated in comparison to an exposure treatment a diary condition and a waiting list
      condition.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
