  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Suffering from Nightmares

          -  Access to internet

          -  A valid e-mail address

          -  Be able to understand Dutch

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe posttraumatic complaints

          -  Severe depression

          -  High anxiety ratings

          -  In therapy for post traumatic stress disorder

          -  Being suicidal

